room_title: Escape room "The Ancient Temple" by Sly Fox Escapes in Colorado Springs
room_address: 5360 N Academy Blvd. Ste 160 Colorado Springs, CO 80918
room_description: Archivists have recently uncovered the journal of Professor Arthur Fact who went missing last year in the jungles of Peru. The journal hints at the location of an undiscovered set of ruins. We need you and your team to pick up the trail and recover the artifacts for study. Be careful! We do not know what happened to Professor Fact and the ruins could be dangerous.
